TTDFT is hosted by the Computational Materials Physics group at University
of Michigan (http://www-personal.umich.edu/~vikramg/), with Vikram Gavini,
Professor of Mechanical Engineering and Materials Science and Engineering,
as the principal investigator broadly overseeing the effort. 'TTDFT authors'
is an all encompassing list of contributors to the TTDFT code.

The code is maintained by Ian C. Lin, the principal developer, who manages the
architecture of the code and the core functionalities under the guidance of the
mentors.

Copyright (c) 2021 The Regents of the University of Michigan

    Principal developers
    ====================
    Ian C. Lin       - University of Michigan, USA

    Mentors
    =======
    Vikram Gavini   - University of Michigan, USA
    Phani Motamarri - Indian Institute of Science, India